Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.20,0:02:15.03,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:19.52,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Hina-chan! Perfect timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:23.28,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to ask you a little favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.52,0:02:28.54,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,You see, the wind yesterday knocked down \Nour scarecrow and broke it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:33.19,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,And, you know, animals have \Nalways liked you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:35.97,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,I know it sounds funny to ask you \Nto take a scarecrow's place,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.97,0:02:37.72,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,but if you'd stick around near the field
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:42.02,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,and attract the animals to you, \Nit'd be a great help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:44.75,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,It's this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.75,0:02:45.93,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.37,0:02:50.44,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I startled you when I just \Nshowed up and started talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:53.19,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:55.89,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,All you have to do is stay right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.89,0:02:57.44,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:03:00.26,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Take a scarecrow's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:05.17,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hina-chan's taking the scarecrow's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.17,0:03:05.70,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:10.98,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,All the animals go straight \Nto her. It's a big help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:14.98,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,She's much more reliable \Nthan any real scarecrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:16.71,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,She sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:23.81,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, thank you for \Nbeing our scarecrow today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:25.10,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:28.10,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a sweet girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:33.10,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I wish we had a scarecrow \Nas cute as you in our fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:37.73,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,It's not often we see \Nsuch a quiet girl, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:41.11,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,She never says a word. Just like a doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:43.63,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,She really is just like a scarecrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:45.39,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,She has the spirit of a pro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:49.37,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,This is just the way I've always been...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:04:01.12,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Standing in the field \Nevery day is exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:04.00,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to do out here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:07.81,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't just tell them \NI'm quitting now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:10.14,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for always helping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.49,0:04:14.74,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, the animals \Ndon't come close anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.74,0:04:18.18,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,so we can concentrate on working \Nin the fields without worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:21.40,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Take these to eat with your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:26.58,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th-Than...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:27.35,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Than?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:28.66,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Than...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:32.00,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:34.42,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hinako. Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:37.12,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You were out late again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:39.89,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Here, use these for dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:41.42,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:48.95,Italics Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, Hinako's been bringing \Nvegetables from somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:50.93,Italics Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,And she's been getting home late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:54.94,Italics Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She couldn't be stealing \Nfrom the fields, could she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:57.37,Italics Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,No, no! That can't be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:04:59.35,Italics Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I trust my little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:04.95,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:08.61,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It's so warm out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:11.58,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It's making me sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.74,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:14.58,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:17.61,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,She's here to be our scarecrow again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:19.08,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,What a big help she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:23.32,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. I'll get her vegetables for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:26.09,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,She'll catch a cold \Nif she stays out here like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:33.09,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! There are so many!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:35.48,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh? What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:38.85,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Am I a jizo statue now? \NWhen did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:42.13,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:44.61,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:47.40,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for being our scarecrow again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:49.11,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,You were a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:55.76,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... These... I... I should \Nalso... tha... than...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:59.45,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry on home before it gets dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.45,0:06:01.17,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Come by again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:07.91,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:11.33,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,This is great, Hinako! \NThanks for always bringing these!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:18.82,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I still haven't been able \Nto thank them for the vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:20.91,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:25.21,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right. All I can do is practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:26.53,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.69,0:06:31.95,sign_9296_75_Hina_Mama_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hina {\c&HF083E0&}Mama
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.69,0:06:31.95,sign_9296_76_My_daughter_is_c,Text,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter is currently wearing \Na costume and talking to a bird...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:53.47,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Tanuki-san, you can be the old man, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:57.00,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,He and his wife are always very kind to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:59.46,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,so I want to be able to thank them properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:01.11,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Help me out, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:03.56,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go. Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:07.07,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,"Hey, Hina-chan! \NWorking hard again today, eh?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:10.57,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,"Hello, sir. Thank you \Nfor all you've done for me."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:13.38,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,"Here are your vegetables for today."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:14.58,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,"Eat them all up."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:19.71,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,"Thank you very much, sir. \NI always enjoy your vegetables."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:20.96,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,"Is that right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.34,0:07:24.01,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,"Yes. My mother always \Nlooks forward to them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:27.30,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, when she sees the \Nvegetables I bring home,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.72,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,she starts planning our meals \Nfor the week with them."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:31.22,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,"Oh?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:35.47,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,"The vegetables from your fields\N are so delicious!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:39.09,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,There! I practiced! \NI said everything perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:39.90,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:40.85,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:44.27,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You did great work again today. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:45.73,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Here, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:50.61,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:52.96,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,See you again tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:55.70,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,The vegetables...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:59.92,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,The vegetables... are delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:03.00,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you for always giving them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.31,0:08:06.50,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I should be thanking you. \NI'll be counting on you again, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:10.61,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yesh! I'll try my besht!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:13.56,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Better try your best to get better \Nat speaking, too, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:25.58,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:35.36,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I'm in Tokyo now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.91,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I have to try my hardest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:40.96,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I have to try hard so I can stand on a stage
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:43.70,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,and learn to talk skillfully to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:46.17,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:51.17,sign_12616_112_It_Begins_Here,Title,0000,0000,0000,,It Begins Here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:50.41,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,The high school's \Ntheater club is on hiatus...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.81,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:03.77,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:04.77,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:07.57,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miss Landlady. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.57,0:09:09.13,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:13.19,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kuu-chan's here, too. \NI'll get breakfast ready right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:18.82,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Go on. Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:20.45,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:26.34,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:28.46,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It's really delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:32.90,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, are you really going to \Nstart a theater troupe, Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:33.34,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:38.45,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Miss Landlady...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:39.56,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:46.11,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,The theater club is on hiatus because \Nthe advisor left on a theater trip, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:47.85,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:50.80,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Why did the advisor leave, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:51.98,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:57.79,Flashback Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:10:01.74,Flashback Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,As I am now, I'm not fit to be your advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:05.56,Flashback Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come back when I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:11.70,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,She said she suddenly felt that \Nher skills had reached a limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:15.26,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She sounds like a passionate teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:18.71,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,What are the other members of the club doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.71,0:10:21.92,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,They're all keeping active in their own ways,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:24.73,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,going out for TV auditions and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:29.30,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,But you've just been practicing by yourself \Nat the park all this time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.78,0:10:34.27,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I want to act with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:36.53,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Landlady...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:40.52,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,She really loves acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:42.03,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:45.66,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you want to get into theater?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:49.18,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.18,0:10:52.17,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you already an actress?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:54.92,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any role \Nyou're particularly good at?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:58.04,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, that would be a scarecrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:04.93,sign_15835_151_Cue_Card,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Cue Card
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:07.43,sign_15943_150_Coffee_Shop_Hito,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Coffee Shop Hitotose
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:11.65,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you want to be in theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:12.85,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:17.17,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, I get so nervous \Nin front of people, and I want to fix that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:19.44,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want to try theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:24.95,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I'm never going to get \Nanywhere this way, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:29.14,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I was nervous \Nat my first performance, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:31.40,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't say my lines very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:33.08,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:36.37,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I was four years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:37.96,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,F-Four?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:41.37,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, you were a \Nchild actress, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:45.05,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,My dad was a stage actor,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.05,0:11:48.52,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,so it happened naturally while \NI helped at his rehearsals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:49.71,Flashback Dialogue,ActressA,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:50.23,Flashback Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:52.49,Flashback Dialogue,ActressA,0000,0000,0000,,Can you grab those props for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:53.69,Flashback Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:58.73,Flashback Dialogue,ActressB,0000,0000,0000,,We've got trouble! The girl \Nplaying Girl A suddenly got sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:02.12,Flashback Dialogue,ActressA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Will we have to cancel today's show?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:04.11,Flashback Dialogue,ActressB,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:07.47,Flashback Dialogue,ActressB,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-chan, can you be a stand-in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:08.62,Flashback Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.88,0:12:13.20,Flashback Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:15.85,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:19.63,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,That would make anyone nervous, child or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:22.60,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Is your father still a stage actor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:24.44,Main Dialogue Top,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cute! Is that food yummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:27.16,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,No, my dad became a guitarist after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:25.99,Main Dialogue Top,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:32.27,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,He travels the world, playing and singing, \Nwhile he manages an apartment building.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:36.31,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, he's apparently \Nplaying the maracas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:42.52,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like quite a free spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:48.03,Note - Copy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\c&HBA2FE3&}1) Slice the apple into rings. \NLeave the peel on!\N2) Coat the inside of a pie pan with butter. \NLay the thawed crust in the pan and trim any excess. \NPoke a few holes in the bottom with\N a fork and chill in the refrigerator for 30 minutes.\NUse a cookie cutter for cute and easy core removal!\NLet the slices sit in salt water. Don't forget to peel them!!\NButter the pie crust!\N30 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:48.03,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBA2FE3&}Cooking Drill: Apple Pie \NIngredients \N1 frozen pie crust \N1 apple \N30g sugar \N1/2 tbsp. lemon juice \NSmall amount of butter \N*Thaw the pie crust at room temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:06.30,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it sounds like it's going to rain soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:09.14,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But it's so sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:10.43,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:13.56,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought we'd be able \Nto dry the laundry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:19.24,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, can you talk to animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:23.15,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, um... \NIt's more like just intuition...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:24.44,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:27.65,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Animals have always been drawn to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.65,0:13:31.68,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Like rabbits, tanuki, boars, deer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:33.95,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,After a while, it just came naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:38.42,Italics Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I think she'd be more suited to \Nthe circus than to theater...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:39.96,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:46.83,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, why don't we try \Nforming a theater troupe after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:47.44,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:52.97,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,What you said earlier made me see \Nthat you really want to be in theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:58.77,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no telling when the school \Ntheater club will start up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:13:59.96,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:01.24,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.24,0:14:01.98,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Kuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:07.74,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,How about we make use of your talent \Nto put on a play with real animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:11.06,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Like {\i1}The Three Little Pigs{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:15.52,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,But that story wouldn't need \Nany human actors, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:17.75,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,That's true... Okay, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:19.58,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe {\i1}Little Red Riding Hood{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:22.05,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever played the grandma would be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:24.37,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,She'd get eaten by the wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.37,0:14:27.30,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, didn't Little Red \NRiding Hood get eaten, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:29.01,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:31.06,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,This is harder than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:33.05,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Miss Landlady...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:37.18,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think I can be an actress?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:42.22,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you can start behind the scenes \Ninstead of jumping right into acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:43.19,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Behind the scenes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:47.44,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot of work to do in a \Ntheater troupe besides just acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:51.72,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Like makeup, set design, script writing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:54.43,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,and putting together props and costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:55.45,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:59.15,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,They also need someone to \Nbook venues for after-parties,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.15,0:15:00.82,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,and people to prepare meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.82,0:15:02.62,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,That's the most important thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:04.58,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I want to work behind the scenes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:07.47,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good with my hands, \Nand I can make clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:10.30,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,No, Mayu-chan, you need \Nto be front and center.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.22,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:13.86,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're as cute as a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:17.12,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,She's right. You have a nice\Nvoice, too. It carries well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:20.39,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan, you'd look great\N in a princess role!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:23.73,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.26,0:15:28.49,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, we haven't \Neven decided we're going to—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:28.49,Main Dialogue Top,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:32.24,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing them talk about it \Nmade it sound kinda fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:35.28,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been interested in \Nthings like scripts, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:37.12,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,And above all,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:39.37,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I want to support Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.87,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Kuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:47.50,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I want to see Mayu-chan \Nplaying a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:50.63,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'm not going to be an actress!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:53.25,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I think you'd be a perfect fit, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:55.05,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:15:59.74,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:02.50,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But we just had breakfast...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:05.15,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little early, but shall we have lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:09.15,Note - Copy,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBA2FE3&} The new fabric softener I bought to try out \Nthe other day smells so nice too... \N\NBuying that was a good choice!\N I'll definitely be buying it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:09.15,Note,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBA2FE3&}The weather's nice today, \Nso it's a perfect day to do the laundry!\N\NWe can dry the bath towels \Nand sheets quickly and fold, fold, fold...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:10.65,sign_23237_249_Today_s_Opening_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Today's Opening Time \N12:30 \NPlease Bear With Us
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.81,0:16:13.01,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But even if we do start a theater troupe,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:17.20,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,is there a place where \Nwe could practice acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:21.32,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking we could make a stage \Nat the back of the coffee shop
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:23.29,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,and use it as a theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:25.73,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You've thought that far ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:27.79,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,You're really into this idea, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:33.92,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought it'd be nice if we could \Nhold regular stage productions here someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:35.18,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,If we could do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:38.33,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,...we'd draw more customers here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:41.52,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You're more shrewd than I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:45.14,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,It would conform with the \Napartment rules, so why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:47.31,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:51.01,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! Residents have to work here in the shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:53.10,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to be in the troupe,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:55.20,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,would you rather work in the coffee shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:58.81,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-W-Wel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:17:03.33,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wel...c-co...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:06.58,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Or would you rather work \Nin the used bookstore?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:15.80,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-Is... Is th-this... \Nthe book you're l-looki—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:14.84,sign_24758_269_The_Setting_Sun,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,100)}The Setting Sun
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:19.87,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'd like to be in the \Ntheater troupe, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:21.00,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Then that settles it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:22.15,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.15,0:17:23.60,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Looking forward to it, principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:26.82,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,A-Actually, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.82,0:17:30.82,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I think you'd make a better principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:33.43,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I only jumped on board with your idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:37.49,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,B-Besides, Aki-chan has to deal \Nwith her work as landlady, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:41.38,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Is working as a landlady really that busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:42.37,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Just accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:47.73,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Me as the principal of the \Ntroupe... I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:48.85,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:54.56,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think anyone wants this theater \Ntroupe to happen more than you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:55.63,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:59.39,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,O... O... O...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:03.11,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll try my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:06.89,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm inexperienced, but I'll be \Ncounting on your support!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:08.97,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,We're looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:13.90,sign_26060_287_Buy_for_Tomorrow,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Buy for Tomorrow: \NCoffee Beans \NFilters
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.97,0:18:10.71,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work hard, Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:12.76,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Can't wait, Principal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:15.90,sign_23237_249_Today_s_Opening_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Today's Opening Time \N14:00 \NPlease Bear With Us
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:18.24,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,If we're going to start a theater troupe,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:20.47,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,we'll need to come up with a troupe name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:22.01,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone have an idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.01,0:18:25.16,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Since it was her idea, it should \Ninclude Hina-chan's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:27.50,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.01,0:18:29.67,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,How about the Hinako Troupe?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:33.29,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Or, for more impact, maybe Hinako Deluxe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:36.80,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe Hinako and Her Merry Band?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:38.69,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:43.04,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A-A... A...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:43.99,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,A?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:48.43,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,The apartment's name, Hitotose...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:51.44,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,So, the Hitotose Troupe?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:54.94,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,The Hitotose Troupe... I like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:57.22,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,The Hitotose Troupe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:18:58.95,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I guess it's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:04.58,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,The Hitotose Troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.90,0:19:08.56,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Now that our troupe has a name,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:10.61,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I need to open the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:11.59,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.66,0:19:16.88,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can I get all of your contact information?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:18.59,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:24.13,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,An SNS might be better than email.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:26.82,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Which SNS do you use?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:28.55,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:33.09,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... what is an SNS?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:34.48,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,We're starting there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:37.26,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Now touch here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:40.24,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Now press this, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:47.49,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Something popped up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:49.75,sign_28472_322_Mom__Kuina__Chia,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Mom \NKuina \NChiaki \NMayuki
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:53.58,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's all of us. You can contact us anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:55.38,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:20:01.03,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:04.27,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to open the shop, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:05.51,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:09.52,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh... C-Can I have more pasta?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:10.89,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You want to eat more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:15.77,sign_29102_330_Mom__Kuina__Chia,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Mom \NKuina \NChiaki \NMayuki
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:23.57,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I got all these new contacts in just one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:26.28,sign_29366_332_Kuina_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Kuina
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:26.28,sign_29366_333_Are_you_awake_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:28.98,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.98,0:20:30.85,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:32.28,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:39.84,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Kuu-chan, you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:41.55,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,The others are here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:44.46,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan! Miss Landlady!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.46,0:20:46.47,Main Dialogue,Mayu,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if we come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:51.92,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, what brings you all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:55.77,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,We were wondering if you'd decided \Nwhat we should do with the troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:21:00.78,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't even know \Nwhere we should start...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:03.63,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you don't have \Nany stage experience yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:08.59,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,So we did some research on theater troupes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.59,0:21:13.25,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,And we found that there's a famous place \Nin Shimokitazawa called Suzuran...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:14.29,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It's this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:15.29,sign_30553_348_Theater_News,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Theater News
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:21.38,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It's a very historical theater that \Neveryone dreams of performing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:22.80,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:23.42,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.70,0:21:26.07,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we try to get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.07,0:21:27.93,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,To someplace that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:31.81,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in. It's always better to dream big.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:35.36,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all for it, too. \NLet's work hard together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:37.94,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.85,0:21:41.40,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Then Suzuran will be our goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:44.15,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Let's put together a great act!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.39,0:21:45.03,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:46.03,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:47.36,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:49.68,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the script to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:49.68,Main Dialogue Top,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:49.68,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:53.62,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:35.26,sign_33685_366_Mistaken_Friend_,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1200,6000)}Mistaken Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.13,0:23:28.34,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It's always better to dream big!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.34,0:23:31.59,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Bigger taiyaki and dorayaki \Nare always more exciting, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:33.22,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,School's about to start, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.22,0:23:37.62,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Just thinking about what awaits \Nin our future makes me so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.62,0:23:39.93,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: "Mistaken Friend."
